channel.title: The Disintegrator
channel.itunes:author: Team
channel.itunes:summary: Harris Edward was a dull guy. Dull in his studies, and nonchalant in his responsibilities. One day a 'disintegration system' finds him and attaches itself to him. The system 'Extracts and Fuses' abstract concepts to his mind. As a trial- he disintegrates the math book, and he becomes a mathematical genius. He is no longer dull. He is no longer a loser. He is no longer worthless. Armed with the ability to solve the biggest problems in the world, will he be able to solve the mystery of his heart? Will he ever find his true love? Find out only on Next eps.
